{"tid":710402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為黨委書記大定CEO大？","createTime":"2018-06-20T17:20:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T01:11:40.000Z","uid":141151,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0331551c038d2c5d9f8594ea5747166ed6c2c970","tid":710402,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T17:20:23.000Z","msg":"廣州港與華為達成戰略合作 共建世界級科技大港<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.wenweipo.com/2018/06/08/IN1806080021.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.wenweipo.com%2F2018%2F06%2F08%2FIN1806080021.htm&d=9XOKsUvGMPZmPgwZpg72AkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=af3847b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.wenweipo.com/2018/06/08/IN1806080021.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n   作為全球領先的信息與通信技術解決方案供應商，華為公司將與廣州港集團進行聯合創新，提供基礎網絡、雲計算、數據中心、物聯網創新等方面的服務，共同推進智慧港口建設<span style=\"color: red;\">。華為公司黨委書記周代琪</span>在簽約致辭時表示：「華為公司期待與廣州港在集團數字化轉型過程中，把港口信息與通信技術（ICT）運營做大、做強，做成全球的標桿。」<br />\n<br />\n唔見CEO出席簽約？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83df8cb1daa183e069f6f51575ed2603188259fe","tid":710402,"uid":29314,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T17:28:19.000Z","msg":"黨委書記大"},{"pid":"f3fd38de5843e8b73ebb895cfe16dceb51d86a57","tid":710402,"uid":75326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T18:26:02.000Z","msg":"CCTVB嘅黨委書記最大"},{"pid":"521f5e43c83e7b75dd54b0e6ddbfdbb419eacfdc","tid":710402,"uid":31841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T18:28:09.000Z","msg":"黨委大<br />\n共狗委員永遠高半格<br />\n=市委&gt;市長一樣"},{"pid":"da3fb9d99c515c232893a599f7d7cc6389bfe2e1","tid":710402,"uid":7206,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T18:39:33.000Z","msg":"同香港一樣<br />\n特首=ceo<br />\n中聯辦主任=黨委書記<br />\n你話邊個大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1db932a8cb5e5e33b10330668ddee419e49ef9","tid":710402,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT