/>\n或者你地可以查下華為CEO 咩身份, 佢係黨入面咁既身份點會細過依個華為書記周代琪"},{"pid":"9965ab7725e65dbf2757a4143e55460d84c004a4","tid":710402,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T12:08:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>CEO 大,<br />\n<br />\n中國有黨委組織既公司CEO 會係果間公司既<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>黨委總書記</strong></span>,<br />\n或者你地可以查下華為CEO 咩身份, 佢係黨入面咁既身份點會細過依個華為書記周代琪</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">全中國全個中共得一個總書記，其他只係叫黨委書記<br />\n一般大陸公司係董事長最大，有時會兼任首席執行官</span>"},{"pid":"4dfbe7b5d866976a53d3ef714ddbc2e0783d038b","tid":710402,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T12:51:59.000Z","msg":"大陸公司只要員工入面有三個黨員就要成立黨支部"},{"pid":"7e9126599ae61f0d4d9473bdb54432f1fe0a00b2","tid":710402,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dfbe7b5d866976a53d3ef714ddbc2e0783d038b","tid":710402,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T12:51:59.000Z","msg":"大陸公司只要員工入面有三個黨員就要成立黨支部"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:03:51.000Z","msg":"中國有8000萬中共黨員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30e88238b840676be2f4031210500c8d232a948","tid":710402,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7e9126599ae61f0d4d9473bdb54432f1fe0a00b2","tid":710402,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dfbe7b5d866976a53d3ef714ddbc2e0783d038b","tid":710402,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T12:51:59.000Z","msg":"大陸公司只要員工入面有三個黨員就要成立黨支部"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:03:51.000Z","msg":"中國有8000萬中共黨員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T05:09:36.000Z","msg":"個黨支部玩野可以整死公司老細，例如捉間公司違規已經大把野捉，大陸公司仔已經玩緊權鬥，老細又要識討好唔同幫派同政府，所以香港人玩政治玩極都係小學雞級。"},{"pid":"b32dbfe5a024a5db7e8e608cc0d4b42dbf6c7182","tid":710402,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9965ab7725e65dbf2757a4143e55460d84c004a4","tid":710402,"uid